::Zardus/Striker::

Zardus spins around as a shot hits Zergling. He looks at Sniper, pulls out 
his launcher, and shoots at him.

Just then Icedeamon lands, asking if he could help. "Yes," Zardus replies, 
"You can take out this meddling maximal...."
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Striker growls, hearing gunfire ahead of him and speeding up.
